(j) By June 15, 2026, and each June 15 thereafter through 2029, the task force
shall produce a report and submit it to the members of the general assembly and the
legislative librarian. It is the intent of this act that the task force's reports are published
on an appropriate page of the general assembly's website.
(k) The task force shall terminate July 1, 2029.
SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 68-211-821, is amended by adding
