SECTION 3. It is the intent of this act that one hundred thousand dollars ($100,000) of
existing funds in the solid waste management fund, created or referenced in title 68, chapter
211, part 8, be allocated to funding the advisory task force on solid waste created by Section 1.
SECTION 4. This act is not an appropriation of funds, and funds must not be obligated
or expended pursuant to this act unless the funds are specifically appropriated by the general
appropriations act.
SECTION 5. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
